# Web Package (`@navo/web`)

## Entry Points

- `web/src/main.tsx` — React mount
- `web/src/App.tsx` — Auth gate, WS lifecycle, event routing
- `web/src/lib/store.ts` — Zustand central state, `applyServerEvent()`
- `web/src/lib/ws-client.ts` — WebSocket client
- `web/src/lib/api.ts` — REST client

## UI Structure

- `web/src/components/` — React components (ChatView, Sidebar, Login, etc.)
- `web/src/components/admin/` — Admin panel tabs and settings
- `web/src/lib/` — Hooks, utilities, E2EE, call controller
- `web/src/platform/` — Web vs Capacitor abstraction (browser, camera, notification)

## Conventions

- React functional components + Zustand (no Redux)
- Tailwind CSS for styling; `cn()` helper for class merging
- Path alias `@/*` → `./src/*`, `@navo/shared` → shared source
- Vite dev proxy: `/api`, `/uploads`, `/ws` → server port (check `.env` PORT vs `vite.config.ts`)
- State changes from server go through `applyServerEvent()` in store.ts

## Doc Reference

Read `docs-src/web/src/<path>.md` before editing matching source under `web/src/`.
